            <description><![CDATA[它家正装20ml的都要129，现在一半的量只要39就能拿下，买上2次的话都快赶上正装的量了 <br> <br>日霜主要添加8%的vc-ip，采用质地是乳液质地，用着清爽好摊开，可以有效抗氧化和淡化黑眼圈💪 <br> <br>晚霜主要添加3%的超A酸➕20%六胜肽，有效抗初老和滋润淡化细纹，坚持用能实现1+1＞2的效果 <br> <br>【39】毕生之研 早C晚A眼霜2ml*5<img style="" src="https://wx3.sinaimg.cn/large/623e5fccgy1h4taexmh2fj20j60j6abo.jpg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><br><br><img style="" src="https://wx4.sinaimg.cn/large/623e5fccgy1h4taeyfakgj20ej0iuq3y.jpg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><br><br><img style="" src="https://wx1.sinaimg.cn/large/623e5fccgy1h4taez7377j20gn0kpdgs.jpg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><br><br><img style="" src="https://wx3.sinaimg.cn/large/623e5fccgy1h4taezyo15j20er0iugmb.jpg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><br><br><img style="" src="https://wx4.sinaimg.cn/large/623e5fccgy1h4taf0pnnzj20ek0j175p.jpg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><br><br><img style="" src="https://wx1.sinaimg.cn/large/623e5fccgy1h4taf1jjmxj20eh0io3zn.jpg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><br><br><img style="" src="https://wx3.sinaimg.cn/large/623e5fccgy1h4taf2bvsbj20eq0id0to.jpg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><br><br><img style="" src="https://wx2.sinaimg.cn/large/623e5fccgy1h4taf33x0bj20ee0i8t9e.jpg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><br><br><img style="" src="https://wx4.sinaimg.cn/large/623e5fccgy1h4taf3v3rmj20ek0hf0tj.jpg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><br><br>]]></description>
